Titolo: Energy Airforce Aim Strike!

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Energy Airforce: aimStrike! is a PlayStation 2 game that focuses on being an authentic flight simulator. All aircraft and weapons used in the game are either existing or prototypes used by the U.S. military. Realistic loads of weapons and fuel (although chaff and flares are unlimited) can be viewed from outside or from a realistic cockpit view. When flying the aircraft in cockpit view, the pilot's leg can be seen depressing appropriately.